---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — EOB Decoder" description="Privacy Policy for EOB Decoder. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F7B8C 0%, #2D4A7A 100%);" class="text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-bold mb-4 leading-tight" style="font-size: 40px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-100" style="font-size: 16px;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-slate">

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">We collect limited information to provide and improve our services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Email address:</strong> If you join our waitlist or sign up for updates, we collect your email address to send you relevant communications.</li>
        <li><strong>EOB text you submit:</strong> When you use the EOB Decoder tool, the text you paste is processed to generate an explanation. We do not store this text on our servers after processing is complete.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> We use Google Analytics to collect anonymized information about how visitors use our site, including pages visited, time on page, and general geographic region. No personally identifiable information is sent to Google Analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>Provide and operate our tools and services</li>
        <li>Send you product updates and relevant communications (email subscribers only)</li>
        <li>Understand how our tools are being used so we can improve them</li>
        <li>Diagnose technical issues and ensure service reliability</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">OpenAI Data Processing</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">The EOB Decoder uses the OpenAI API to process and explain the text you submit. When you use this tool, your input is sent to OpenAI for processing. OpenAI's data usage policies apply to this processing. OpenAI states that API inputs are not used to train their models by default. We encourage you to review <a href="https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OpenAI's Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">We use a small number of cookies for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Rate limiting:</strong> A session cookie is used to enforce fair usage limits on our API tools.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Analytics cookies help us understand aggregate usage patterns. These cookies do not identify you personally.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">We do not use advertising cookies or sell cookie data to third parties.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">We share your information only with the following third parties, and only as necessary to operate our services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li><strong>OpenAI:</strong> EOB text you submit is sent to OpenAI for processing via their API.</li>
        <li><strong>Web3Forms:</strong> If you use a contact form on our site, your submission is processed via Web3Forms to deliver it to us.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Anonymized usage data is shared with Google Analytics to help us understand site usage.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to any other third parties.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>The right to access the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>The right to request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>The right to request deletion of your information</li>
        <li>The right to opt out of marketing communications at any time</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at the email address below.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:amitsharma00261@gmail.com" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">amitsharma00261@gmail.com</a></p>

      <div class="bg-[#F0FAFB] border border-[#0F7B8C]/20 rounded-xl p-6 mt-10">
        <p class="text-[#334155] text-sm leading-relaxed">This policy may be updated from time to time. Continued use of EOB Decoder after changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy. Last updated: July 2026.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
